</li>
<li>"Themes in Kant's Moral Philosophy." In Eckhart Forster, ed., <i>Kant's Transcendental Deductions: The Three Critiques and the Opus postumum</i>, pp. 81–113, 253–256. Stanford Series in Philosophy. Studies in Kant and German Idealism. Stanford, California: Stanford University Press, 1989.</li>
</ul>
